data.description: Remodeled beauty with a brand new BRIGHT and OPEN KITCHEN in the historic district!!!! NEW ROOF!!! Newer AC! Perfect floorplan with 3 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms. You will love this quaint home in the historic district. Lots of potential with this well thought out plan. Two of the bedrooms have their on bathroom and all bedrooms have walk in closests!!!! The third bedroom is also very large and private with a bathroom close by. Come see it today!
